machinevision-desc: Interfaces with internal and external machine vision service providers and stores results for usage on-wiki.
machinevision-machineaidedtagging-intro: Review suggested tags of [[c:Commons:Depicts|depicted objects]] in images. Only user-confirmed tags are added to images. For more information, check out the [[c:Commons:Structured_data/Computer-aided_tagging|project page]] and [[give feedback]] on how to make this tool more helpful!
